{"tid":179984,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"畀湯怡掉晒新人獎！洪卓立嚇呆嗌心痛","createTime":"2017-03-30T15:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T18:42:17.000Z","uid":11345,"like":22,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe8fc9e6c5cd9d9b0ac7146ea0e960a1a436613","tid":179984,"uid":11345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T15:23:49.000Z","msg":"歌手洪卓立（Ken）到電台宣傳新歌《帶着骨灰去旅行》，他表示近日是帶着眼淚去旅行，因為發生了一件<span style=\"color: red;\">不幸的事</span>：「我將之前拎到嘅新人獎放喺屋企，近日要搬屋就執咗拎番出嚟，有一箱嘢我話唔要，但Kathy（女友湯怡）就誤會咗係裝獎嗰箱，佢就全部掉晒。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Ken指晚上回家後發現所有新人獎項都不見了，即時嚇到目定口呆</span>：「佢知道掉錯咗就即刻着衫落街去垃圾房搵，跟住喊晒番嚟&hellip;我其實都好唔開心，但要安慰咗佢先，我就話再攞過囉，但其實新人獎冇得再攞過，一係整個新組合再嚟，但真係<span style=\"color: red;\">全部清晒</span>。Kathy第二朝起身後再落去搵，佢話唔夠膽返屋企，但冇辦法。」又指經此教訓後，會在箱子上寫清楚是裝甚麼東西，而且會自己掉垃圾。問到女友之後可有更加小鳥依人？Ken笑言有改善，而且女友不會對他黑面，更願意出錢買電子遊戲給他。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330141351949-0330_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170330190618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330141351949-0330_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170330190618&h=dfb0aade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330141351949-0330_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170330190618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330141351949-0330_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170330190618&h=5e95cff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170330/bkn-20170330141351949-0330_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170330%2Fbkn-20170330141351949-0330_00862_001.html&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=47db7d34\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170330/bkn-20170330141351949-0330_00862_001.html